description: Retrieves the IPSet specified by the ipSetId.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the detector that is associated with the IPSet. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

parameters.name: IpSetId
parameters.description: The unique ID of the IPSet to retrieve.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The user-friendly name for the IPSet.

nested_items.name: Format
nested_items.description: The format of the file that contains the IPSet.

nested_items.name: Location
nested_items.description: The URI of the file that contains the IPSet.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of IPSet file that was uploaded.
